  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>Published: January 11, 2019</p>\n<p>As previously planned and <a class=\"external-link\" title=\"Follow link\" href=\"/w/delayed-disabling-tls-1-0-for-inbound-traffic-on-liferay-services-and-websites-Delayed-Disabling-TLS-1-0-for-Inbound-Traffic-on-Liferay-Services-and-Websites\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-hs-link-id=\"0\">announced</a>, Liferay has disabled TLS 1.0 for inbound traffic on Liferay services and websites.</p>\n<p>Please navigate to the <a class=\"external-link\" title=\"Follow link\" href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/360019140811\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-hs-link-id=\"0\">Knowledge Base</a> for a list of affected Liferay systems and services, as well as mitigation instructions for deployments.</p>"
      },
